 indicates the phonon-mediated medium coupled\nBCS superconductors. The obtained potential results in present calculation\ncould provide a significant movement for future studies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 21 Sep 2018 16:46:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-24"}
