ima c to be $3.13~{M_ \\oplus } \\le {m_c} \\le 70.7~{M_\n\\oplus }$ when $1.27~{M_ \\oplus } \\le {m_b} \\le 1.6~{M_ \\oplus }$, if\n${i_{mutual}} \\le {50^{\\circ}}$ and $\\Delta \\Omega = 0^{\\circ}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 21 Sep 2018 17:04:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-30"}
