 perspectives for realizing\ndistinct instances of generalized Gibbs ensembles in optical lattice-based\narchitectures.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 21 Sep 2018 18:46:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 15 Jul 2019 04:28:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-02"}
